                 </p>
                </div>
           </div>
           <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-4">
            <div class="contentCard">
                <h4>Download Free</h4>
                <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <p>Virtual Classroom delivers quality audio / video simply through the web-browser 
                  so you no longer have to spend time on software. 
                </p>
               </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-4">
            <div class="contentCard">
                <h4>Video Recording</h4>
                <i class="fa fa-play-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <p>Teachers and schools see recording as an opportunity to ensure teacher quality and 
                  help student review.
                </p>
               </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-4">
            <div class="contentCard">
                <h4>Assessment Submission</h4>
                <i class="far fa-newspaper"></i>
                <p>It is a digital platform which is designed to provide a complete 
                  environment to develop, manage and submit any assignment for all.
                </p>
               </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-4">
            <div class="contentCard">
                <h4>Online Examination</h4>
                <i class="far fa-edit"></i>
                <p>Virtual Classroom is the online 
                  exam system with best in class features and data security. 
                </p>
               </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-4">
            <div class="contentCard">
                <h4>Post to class Stream</h4>
                <i class="fas fa-address-card"></i>
                <p>Students and Teachers can post and comment to the class stream
                  in this virtual system.
                </p>
               </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </section>
       <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-form">
          <div class="contact-image">
              <img src="https://image.ibb.co/kUagtU/rocket_contact.png" alt="rocket_contact"/>
          </div>
          <form method="POST" action="/contact">
              <h3>Drop Us a Message</h3>
              <%if(messages.error){%>
                <p class="alert alert-danger"><%=messages.error%></p>
                <%}%>
                <%if(messages.success){%>
                  <div class=" alert alert-success" role="alert">
                    <span><%=messages.success%></span>
                  </div>
                  <%}%>
             <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-md-6">
                      <div class="form-group">
                          <input type="text" name="Name" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Name *" value="" />
                      </div>
                      <div class="form-group">
                          <input type="email" name="Email" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Email *" value="" />
                      </div>
                      <div class="form-group">
                          <input type="text" name="Phone" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Phone Number *" value="" />
                      </div>
                      
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-6">
                      <div class="form-group">
                          <textarea name="txtMsg" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Message *" style="width: 100%; height: 150px;"></textarea>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="submit" name="btnSubmit" class="btnContact" value="Send Message" />
            </div>
          </form>
</div>
